    subtopic: "Childhood Obesity Assessment",
    stem: `Parents of an 11-year-old boy have brought him to your clinic for assessment because they believe he is obese. On examination, his weight and height are on 90 and 50 percentiles for sex- and age-matched growth charts respectively. Which one of the following is the most appropriate investigation to consider for him?`,
