    topic: "Paediatrics",
    subtopic: "Pertussis management and contact prophylaxis",
    stem: `Paul, aged 4 months, is diagnosed with pertussis. The father is an engineer and the mother a housewife. They both have completed childhood vaccination against pertussis. Paul has a 5-year-old sister. Which one of the following is the most appropriate management plan to consider for Paul's parents regarding pertussis?`,
