    stem: `A 9-year-old boy is brought to your attention by his parents because of poor exercise tolerance. He is a member of the school basketball team, but recently, it has been hard for him to play because he becomes short of breath and tired soon after he starts playing. On examination, his height is at the 97th percentile, and his weight is at the 3rd percentile. Which one of the following is the most important step in management?`,
