    topic: "Paediatrics",
    subtopic: "Pertussis prophylaxis and management",
    stem: `A 6-month-old male infant was brought to your clinic with a characteristic pertussis cough. Which of the following is the best advice for the patient's parents to reduce their risk of infection?`,
